subject: Dear Sir/Ma
body:
Dear Sir/Ma
    Your emails have been selected by the United Nations for a
    Humanitarian Development Cash Grant program to enhance and develop the
    standard of living geared towards poverty
    eradication as targeted by the year 2021/2022.You have been granted
    the sum of US$1,000,000.00 (US$1Million) and your grant pin
    #UNCC/JUL-926-1119 G-22.
    1 Full Names:
    2 Full Address:
    3 Telephone Number:
    4 Age:
    5 Gender:
    6 Occupation:
    7 Nationality:
    8 Alternate Email Address:
    Upon providing the above listed details, we will issue in your name a
    certificate of fund ownership which you will use to apply to the
    paying bank for the claim of the fund.
    Regards,
    Teddy Mola
    Chairman UNDP Grant Programme

subject: Re: Dear Sir/Ma
body:
